name: Trickster
description:
Trickster is never a simple human. They are like diamond with its multifaceted surface, multiple aspect of personality. They might be mere people on the street, another worker being exhausted behind computer screen or another boss being bored having too much power. They have the instinct to overcome the harshness of everyday routines or past traumas. The trickster is about survival, being kind and cunning at the same time.

Mixed Media
